Package org.hibernate.query.results.complete

Support for immutable result/fetch builder graph nodes built from static sources such as JPA's SqlResultSetMapping or `hbm.xml` mapping ``. The differentiation from org.hibernate.query.results.dynamic is that here we have up-front knowledge of the complete mapping graph and can perform optimized resolution process
